All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpContent
final class GZipContent
extends AbstractHttpContent

Serializes another source of HTTP content using GZip compression.

Implementation is not thread-safe.

Author:
Yaniv Inbar

Method Detail

writeTo

public void writeTo(java.io.OutputStream out)
             throws java.io.IOException
Writes the content to the given output stream and closes the output stream.

The output stream is closed by calling DeflaterOutputStream.close() to avoid a resource leak caused due to an instance of Deflater being left open. See Bug 61 for more information.

java.io.IOException

Sets the media type to use for the Content-Type header, or null if unspecified.
